data.description: Gorgeous Craftsman home w/ a touch of historical charm, Spacious 4 Bdrm. Newer roof, gutters & paint. Vinyl windows that let in natural light, Kitchen w/newer SS appliances, durable concrete countertops & a breakfast nook. Luxury formal dining room. Large living room w/a 150” projector screen & wired for surround sound & projector. Perfect for hosting memorable gatherings. This property offers 2169sqft of living space, large unfinished basement w/ endless opportunities to customize. A large lot size w/a fully fenced front yard offering a safe space for your pets to play. A good sized deck off the kitchen. A driveway w/detached carport & attached garage. 13 month home warranty. Don't miss out on this magnificent property.
